description: Heals all the undead in the party
note:
<Custom Target Eval>
  for (var i = 0; i < allies.aliveMembers().length; ++i) {
    var member = allies.aliveMembers()[i];
	var states = member.states();
	// Loop through each state.
	for (var j = 0; j < states.length; ++j) {
	  // Get the currently looped state.
	  var state = states[j];
	  if (state && state.id === 11)
	  {
		  targets.push(member)
	  }
	}
  }
  </Custom Target Eval>
